Update line with regular expression
- name: Update Cluster Name
  lineinfile:
    path: "{{ScyllaConfigFile}}" 
    regex: '^#cluster_name:*|^cluster_name:'
    line: 'cluster_name: {{ClusterName}}'

How to use a public keypair .pem file for ansible playbooks?
ssh-agent bash
ssh-add ~/.ssh/keypair.pem
